status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$
\backslash
sigma = 5.67 W
\backslash
e{-8}  W.
 m^{-2}.
 K^{-4}$
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Un cuerpo que no es un radiador ideal satisface la misma ley general pero
 con un coeficiente 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$a$
\end_layout

\end_inset

 < 1 :
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

